ygData.messageBody:
Sup my friends? Just informing all whom are
interested that a guild has been formed and Elf Rangers are
welcome to submit forms. Although the page is just about
finished, I have currently forgotten the webpage (roomate
isn't here at the moment to remind me). You can reach
me at Job18@.... Although the guild is Elf,
the rangers stand a better shot at getting excepted
and an office cause of the history of the
guild.<br>Thanks for your time,<br>Tancred
